text: The Main road 26 is an east–west direction Secondary class main road in the road in the valley of a Sajó river, that connects the Main road 3 change to the border of Slovakia. The road is long.Magyarország, autóatlasz 1:200.000, Honvédelmi Minisztérium Térképészeti Kht., . The road, as well as all other main roads in Hungary, is managed and maintained by Magyar Közút, state owned company. ==See also== * Roads in Hungary ==Sources== ==External links== * Hungarian Public Road Non-Profit Ltd.
